<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我諗佢都真係發緊夢</span></span>"},{"pid":"ace59eb7481b48387e0fa4e18607355a83c6eab0","tid":647671,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e02af2d20cef41d93420962e07e61684ad24d58","tid":647671,"uid":25754,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"62c1a3c7590f13ed5502dd13c9e83d108c27c736","tid":647671,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"其實一切都係發夢 連avengers其實都係假架<br />\n一切冇存在過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:21:11.000Z","msg":"Tony stark只係個自閉症兒童<br />\n美國隊長雷神變形俠醫奇異博士係庇護工場d同事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"bucky 只係美國隊友想像出嚟既幻覺朋友"},{"pid":"41a09525e051a5bc88464b1d4972f4c5478e3edd","tid":647671,"uid":181416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace59eb7481b48387e0fa4e18607355a83c6eab0","tid":647671,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e02af2d20cef41d93420962e07e61684ad24d58","tid":647671,"uid":25754,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"62c1a3c7590f13ed5502dd13c9e83d108c27c736","tid":647671,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"其實一切都係發夢 連avengers其實都係假架<br />\n一切冇存在過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:21:11.000Z","msg":"Tony stark只係個自閉症兒童<br />\n美國隊長雷神變形俠醫奇異博士係庇護工場d同事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"bucky 只係美國隊友想像出嚟既幻覺朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff1088dd5355c8da2f12202cf5c688957ea53f8","tid":647671,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eff25c62e0174